name: B0761  Labradorite, Freshwater Pearls & Sterling Silver
description: When you slip this gorgeous labradorite & pearl bracelet on, you know you are wearing one fine piece of jewelry!  The size of this bracelet is substantial at 1 inch wide.  The large, lustrous grey button pearls shimmer amidst the luminous labradorite rectangles.  A large, round .925 sterling silver toggle clasp completes the 7 1/2" bracelet.

name: B1265 Vintage Silverware Bracelet
description: Vintage silver-plated flatware handles are re-purposed to beautiful bracelets!  This particular bracelet is made using a vibrant blue marble jasper stone with faceted blue agate beads on both sides.  I attempted to finish this bracelet to 7 1/2", but given that the handle is curved (and inflexible) you may need a length adjustment.  I will be happy to do that for you.

name: N1224 Lake Agate Necklace
description:
These Lake Agate oval beads are flat and smooth, primarily brown with subtle shades of grey-blue and soft greens, creating a rich dimension of nature's colors.  The necklace is a combination of other agates and jaspers, including two beautiful Tibetan carved agate rounds accent beads.  Length is adjustable 18 1/2" to 20 1/2" with a large lobster claw clasp.  

NOTE:  Lake Agate stones are approx. 1 1/2" long.

name: N0237  Turquoise Magnasite Necklace & (Optional) Earrings & Bracelet
description:
This necklace is just plain fun!  The Turquoise Magnasite flat ovals are approx 3/4" x 1/2" and have very nice veins.  The spotted Horn rondelles add to the whimsy of this necklace.  Gun metal accent beads and a pretty hook clasp complete the strand of 20" length.

Click on picture of the matching Earrings (E1234), 1 3/4" long, & Bracelet (B1186), 76 1/2" long, which are also available.

name: N1190  Hard Candy Cracked Agate Necklace
description: What a fun hard-candy-colored necklace to wear everywhere!  These 10mm Cracked Agate faceted beads sparkle with yummy goodness.  Hematite spacers and a silvery focal bead hang nicely from a smooth gunmetal chain.  A lobster claw clasp fastens the necklace to an adjustable length, up to 22" long.

name: N1209  Flower Jasper & Fire Cherry Quartz Necklace
description: Flower Jasper rounds create a 3" focal bar, from which five 1 1/2" dangles of Pink Ocean Agate, Fire Cherry Quartz and tiny Freshwater Pearls sweetly hang.  The blushing shades of coral and creamy peach sparkle from a mix of smooth and faceted stones.  The gunmetal wire and chain make an adjustable necklace of 23" - 26" long with a lobster claw clasp.

name: B1028  Blue Opal & Aquamarine Bracelet
description:
Three 12mm Blue Opal rounds are front and center in this exquisite shades-of-blue bracelet.  Sterling Silver "wheels" separate large Aquamarine chips nestled on each side.  The simple toggle clasp and finishings are also .925 Sterling Silver.  Measures:  7 1/2" long.

Contact me if you would like a length adjustment.

name: B1180  Smoky Quartz Nuggets & Black Onyx Bracelet
description:
Large Smoky Quartz faceted nuggets sparkle warmly between chubby Black Onyx rondelles.  This bracelet is a stunning black and brown fashion statement.  The largest nugget is approx. 3/8" x 3/4" long.  The flat toggle clasp and finishings are .925 Sterling Silver.  Measures:  7 1/2" long

Please contact me if you need a length adjustment.

name: B1075  Lapis & Sterling Silver Bracelet
description:
Three fine strands of Lapis bricks are accented with tiny Sterling Silver cubes.  Each strand is approx. 1/8" thick, with smooth edges and a luxurious touch.  The lovely tulip toggle clasp closes securely to a 7 1/2" length.  Clasp, accent beads and finishings are all .925 Sterling Silver.

Contact me with questions or for a length adjustment.

name: B0681  Dumorterite, Chrysocolla, Iolite & Freshwater Pearls Bracelet
description:
This gorgeous bracelet is a blend of blues and greens and sandy-beige pearls.  It's a double-strand bracelet woven through double-drilled Dumorterite stones.  Small Sterling Silver accent beads fill in nicely oozing elegance.  The easy-to-close toggle clasp and finishings are all .925 Sterling Silver.  Measures:  7 1/2"

Please contact me if you need a length adjustment.

name: B1233  Freshwater Coin Pearls & Pink River Stone Bracelet
description:
You will first notice the spectacular luster in these white Freshwater Coin Pearls!  These pearls are approx. 8mm in diameter and sparkle with a tiny seed bead separating each one.  The Pink River Stone rondelles add a soft, beach-inspired theme to this bracelet.  The small leaf toggle clasp closes neatly to a 7 1/2" length.

I will happily adjust the bracelet length to suit you.

name: B0984  African Map Jasper Bracelet
description:
African Map Jasper is such a distinctively different stone.  Colors of the desert in many shades of khaki create a color-by-number affect of soft, creamy hues.  The unusual double-drilled stones lye comfortably on your wrist and close with an easy toggle clasp.

7 3/4" long.

Contact me if you need a length adjustment.

name: B1177  Cracked Agate & Black Onyx Bracelet
description:
This pretty bracelet is made up of 8mm faceted beads in various shades of mauve/plum, some of which are quite pale.  There are veins in many of these stones adding interest to the nature's beauty, and a tiny charlotte seed bead separating each one for added sparkle.  The easy toggle clasp, accent beads and finishings are all .925 sterling silver.  7 3/4" long.

Please contact me if you need a length adjustment.

name: N1178  Dalmatian Jasper Necklace & (Optional) Bracelet & Earrings
description:
These flat and smooth Dalmatian Jasper stones are accented with round Wood Jasper and Blackstone beads to make a daytime-to-evening smashing look!  Lobster claw clasp closes to a 3" chain to make this necklace adjustable 18" - 21" long.

Click photos of optional Bracelet (#B1179), 7 3/4" long.

Please let me know if you need a size adjustment.

name: N0468  Dream Jasper Necklace & Optional Bracelet & Earrings
description:
The "dreamy" shades of blue in these Jasper stones are captured between two .925 Sterling Silver accent beads.  Blue Fire Feldspar and small seed beads complete the strand of 20 1/2".  The lovely hook clasp, accent beads and finishings are all .925 Sterling Silver.

Contact me if you need a complimentary length adjustment.

Click pictures of Bracelet (B1081) 7 1/2" long & Earrings (E0486) 2" long which are also available.

name: B1229  Combo of Freshwater Pearls Bracelet & Earrings (Optional)
description:
Lustrous 10mm white coin pearls combine beautifully with soft gray coin pearls.  Three large  white keishi pearls accent the strand.  A stunning .925 Sterling Silver toggle clasp close this bracelet to a 7 1/2" length.  All pearls are authentic freshwater pearls.  Clasp, accent beads and finishings are .925 Sterling Silver.

Click on picture of matching Earrings (E1230), 1 3/8" long.

Contact me for complimentary length adjustment.
